{"id":2,"name":"EV002","note":"新版代码适配烹饪小游戏","pages":[{"conditions":{"actorId":1,"actorValid":false,"itemId":1,"itemValid":false,"selfSwitchCh":"A","selfSwitchValid":false,"switch1Id":1,"switch1Valid":false,"switch2Id":1,"switch2Valid":false,"variableId":1,"variableValid":false,"variableValue":0},"directionFix":false,"image":{"characterIndex":0,"characterName":"","direction":2,"pattern":0,"tileId":0},"list":[{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[90]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"black",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[0]},{"code":129,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,0,false]},{"code":129,"indent":0,"parameters":[4,1,false]},{"code":205,"indent":0,"parameters":[-1,{"list":[{"code":29,"parameters":[4],"indent":null},{"code":30,"parameters":[3],"indent":null},{"code":0}],"repeat":false,"skippable":false,"wait":true}]},{"code":505,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"code":29,"parameters":[4],"indent":null}]},{"code":505,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"code":30,"parameters":[3],"indent":null}]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>迷路迷境久违地热闹起来，妖精们对着香喷喷的悬锋炖菜大快朵颐，打开了话匣子。听着小妖精们七嘴八舌地讲白厄小时候的糗事，万敌手上的动作没停，嘴角却极轻地动了一下。这个笨蛋，从小就不让人省心。"]},{"code":242,"indent":0,"parameters":[10]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>万敌向妖精们分享了自己在外行军的故事，和黄金裔们如何按照昔涟和阿格莱雅制定的计划，接力抗击来古士的故事，妖精们听得激动又紧张。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>为了不破坏开心热闹的气氛，万敌模糊了结局：“现在，我和战友们准备最后一战。昔涟说还有点时间，就让我过来找你们。之后我和白厄会合，就能把敌人一举拿下。”"]},{"code":241,"indent":0,"parameters":[{"name":"dream and biskit","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,1]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["<wrap>“好开心呀，好像在哪个梦里也有过这样热热闹闹的宴席”，妖精们赞美道。随着食物见底，这场偶然的小宴席渐渐散场。妖精村长指挥小妖精们收拾打扫，她则飘来向万敌道谢。"]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[28,28,1]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[26,26,0]},{"code":121,"indent":0,"parameters":[200,200,0]},